CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 18, 1961, pg. 19 reads: Swing Your Partner - Loendi Club took on the air of an old-fashioned barn recently when the Loendi Ladies Auxlliary [sic] sponsored a square dance in club's parlors...Carl Redwood, wearing a gay checked shirt, can be seen in the second photo [last] "calling the figures for the dancers...-Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Men, including Carl Redwood wearing plaid shirt, and women, square dancing in Loendi Club, sponsored by the Loendi Ladies Auxiliary
